{"tid":545101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天氣太凍　深圳多班高鐵停駛","createTime":"2018-01-30T07:45:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T04:07:17.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"574e994aec370d2d0cd477cb53df12b0ad802793","tid":545101,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:45:31.000Z","msg":"雖然廣州未有下雪，但華南在寒流下氣溫已直線下降，深圳北站今日多班高鐵列車停駛，包括開往西安北站、長沙南站、廣州南站的G818、G6030、G6218和G6204列車，及由福田站開往懷化南站的G6146列車。<br />\n<br />\n深圳北站負責人表示，已購買停駛列車車票的乘客，可在不遲於原本乘車日期起30天內（含當日），辦理全額退票手續，不收取手續費，持紙質車票的旅客可到任意車站窗口辦理退票，呼籲大家合理安排退票時間，不要集中前往火車站退票。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180130/s00004/1517289866936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180130%2Fs00004%2F1517289866936&d=inXPCrULM1zxCKPcBZ3uEARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ad8e066a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180130%2Fs00004%2F1517289866936&h=89fc3cea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180130/s00004/1517289866936</a>"},{"pid":"791657702e3fcb339fa1079e91cbdc4836dd636d","tid":545101,"uid":41737,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:47:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3867eb5cceef9909de626fe0d659b313d92b1eca","tid":545101,"uid":41818,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:48:02.000Z","msg":"無落雪停乜Q"},{"pid":"c6d4e5c549119ca9ed15717ded1a177c252fe267","tid":545101,"uid":45285,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:49:26.000Z","msg":"真心唔識，天氣凍但無落雪，點解會停駛？？？？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6b014c289c5b84dfcdbbfb5081cc6c4ac63f66","tid":545101,"uid":83016,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T07:51:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心唔識，天氣凍但無落雪，點解會停駛？？？？ <img src=\